headline: Why Investors Were Eager to Climb Aboard American Express Today
summary: Storied credit card giant American Express (NYSE: AXP) rode the express train to profit on Thursday.  On news of several analyst price target increases, the company's stock zoomed almost 2% higher on the day.  What helped was that not one, not two, but three analysts upped their fair value assessments of AmEx stock.
